import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Link } from 'docz'

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"getting-started"}}>{`Getting Started`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`It’s consistent`}</MDXTag>{`. The way components are built and managed follows a predictable pattern.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`It’s self-contained`}</MDXTag>{`. Your design system is treated as a standalone dependency.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`It’s reusable`}</MDXTag>{`. You’ve built components so they can be reused in many contexts.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`It’s accessible`}</MDXTag>{`. Applications built with your design system are usable by as many people as possible, no matter how they access the web.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`It’s robust`}</MDXTag>{`. No matter the product or platform to which your design system is applied, it should perform with grace and minimal bugs.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="hr" components={components}></MDXTag>
<Link to="/src-components-buttons-button">Go Button</Link>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
